text:
This is one of the famous duck rice stall in bukit Panjang area, ordered the kwai teow with yellow noodle, added a liver - price is only $3.70, portion is just nice, the taste is just nice for me not salty at all, will come back again
Highly recommended - must try
Duck rice was okay. Just that they are stingy to give you some slices of cucumber so be aware.
